      "text": "分手才是永恒",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 30.68,
      "time_str": "00:30.680",
      "text": "当你出现在我的天空",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 37.29,
      "time_str": "00:37.290",
      "text": "你的头发在风中飘动",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 42.48,
      "time_str": "00:42.480",
      "text": "当我转过身找不到你影踪",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 50.47,
      "time_str": "00:50.470",
      "text": "你只留下一道彩虹",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 56.2,
      "time_str": "00:56.200",
      "text": "都知道是分开的结局",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 64.16,
      "time_str": "01:04.160",
      "text": "就算重逢也无法再继续",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 69.82,
      "time_str": "01:09.820",
      "text": "难道是命运捉弄了我一生",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 77.34,
      "time_str": "01:17.340",
      "text": "而我不得不承认",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 83.08,
      "time_str": "01:23.080",
      "text": "松开你的手 让你走",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 91.09,
      "time_str": "01:31.090",
      "text": "没有人会知道 我的感受",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 96.81,
      "time_str": "01:36.810",
      "text": "若有一天 你会发现",
